commit.message:
ipa-fnsummary.c (pass_data_ipa_fn_summary): Use TV_IPA_FNSUMMARY.


	* ipa-fnsummary.c (pass_data_ipa_fn_summary): Use
	TV_IPA_FNSUMMARY.
	* timevar.def (TV_IPA_FNSUMMARY): Define.

From-SVN: r250236
